The width of this gap evolves in time according to

\begin{equation}
\label{eq:gap_1var_app}
    \Delta^{\text{GAP}}_{\text{fin}}(t;\sigma)=\frac{\sigma^2(1+\alpha_m^{-1/2})^{2}}{t+\sigma^2(1+\alpha_m^{-1/2})^{2}}.
